3. Integration Requirements



→ ML Model Integration

• Load pre-trained model (.pkl or .h5 format)

• Real-time inference at low latency



→ Database

• SQLite / PostgreSQL for storing:

• traffic logs

• threat history

• model predictions



→ WebSockets for Real-Time Dashboard

• Real-time event streaming

• Threat updates appear instantly on UI



